              "choices": [
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_1",
                  "content": "Having each worker assigned to a specific task is a component of bureaucracy."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "Without written rules, a division of labor is unable to foster a bureaucracy."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "In general, when an organization divides the labor, the bureaucracy disintegrates."
                },
                {
